tpp registration
│
├── Reads → env.json (your config)
│
├── Calls → OP’s Certificate Generator API
│     ↓
│     Receives → QWAC & QSEAL certs + keys
│     ↓
│     Saves → PEM files under ./cert/
│
├── Validates certificates (optional check)
│
├── Calls → OP’s TPP Registration API
│     ↓
│     Receives → client_id, client_secret
│     ↓
│     Saves → config/clientinfo.json
│
└── Returns → “TPP registration completed successfully!”
